<% content_for :title, "Terms of Service" %>

<div class="row justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-lg-7">
    <h1 class="h3 fw-bold mb-1">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-muted small mb-4">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="vstack gap-4">
      <section>
        <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Acceptable use</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">You may use Serendipity only for lawful personal purposes — keeping track of your relationships and scheduling catch-ups with people you know. You may not use the service to send unsolicited messages, scrape data, or for any commercial purpose without our written permission.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Community standards</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">All content you enter — contact names, event notes, tags, and your profile — must comply with these standards:</p>
        <ul class="text-muted">
          <li><strong>No harassment or hate speech.</strong> Do not enter content that targets, demeans, or threatens any person or group.</li>
          <li><strong>No spam or impersonation.</strong> Do not create fake contacts or events, or impersonate another person.</li>
          <li><strong>No profanity or obscene content.</strong> Keep names, notes, and tags professional and respectful.</li>
          <li><strong>No illegal content.</strong> Do not enter anything that violates applicable laws.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Your data</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">We store only the data you provide to run the Serendipity service. We do not sell or share your data. For full details, see our <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_path %>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Account termination</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms. You may also delete your account at any time from your account settings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">To report a violation or ask a question about these terms, email us at <a href="mailto:stayintouch.cs396@gmail.com">stayintouch.cs396@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-4"><%= link_to "← Back", :back, class: "text-muted small" %></p>
  </div>
</div>
